sri harikathe ( kannada : ಶ ರೀ ಹರಿಕಥೆ ) is a 2010 indian kannada language romantic-thriller film directed by dayal padmanabhan .   the film stars sri murali , pooja gandhi , radhika gandhi and naveen krishna in pivotal roles .   the film is jointly produced by s. a. chinne gowda and m. n. kumar .   the film release co-coincided with another sri murali film sihi gaali on 12 march 2010 .